{
  "name": "Animate Hair",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/fallen_fey.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your hair grows long and animates. You may activate the following abilities as fey-blessings:</p>\n<p><strong>Entangling Locks:</strong> Any hostile creature must succeed on a Reflex save any time it becomes or starts its turn adjacent to you. A creature that fails its save cannot move away from you without first succeeding on a Strength check or an Escape Artist check against your sphere DC made as a move action.</p>\n<p><strong>Grasping Tresses:</strong> You may use your hair to grab objects. Your hair grants a slam attack (primary, 1d4 Medium, 1d3 Small, bludgeoning damage), but may not assist in wielding weapons, activate magic items, or wield a shield. It may hold items and as a swift action you can use it to draw a sheathed or hidden weapon, ready a shield, retrieve a stored item, load a crossbow, open a door, pick up an unattended item within your natural reach, sheathe or store an item, or take other non-offensive actions involving manipulating objects.</p>\n",
